Black Friday 2018 takes place on 23 November, but instead of just having deals on one day many South African retailers have launched week-long promotions. Game, for example, is already running its Black Friday Warmup Deals promotion, which lasts for 10 days – from 14-23 November. Esquire, in turn, is offering great tech deals during their “Rainbow Week” between 19-23 November. Many other retailers have also launched early Black Friday deals, with a strong focus on gadgets and other tech products. Here are some of the best early Black Friday tech specials which are available in South Africa.                                    